      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project car or a donor for parts. The engine is currently non-operational, and there are visible signs of significant wear and tear throughout, including substantial rust on the frame and body panels. The interior has suffered from neglect, with torn upholstery and missing trim pieces. While it was once a reliable machine, it will require a complete mechanical overhaul and extensive bodywork to return to the road. Please come prepared with a trailer, as the car is not drivable in its current state.",
