    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit remains naturally aspirated, utilizing its factory individual throttle bodies for crisp throttle response. The critical VANOS system has been professionally overhauled with upgraded seals and rattle kits to ensure variable valve timing precision. The drivetrain features the desirable Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission paired with a GKN limited-slip differential. To address common platform weaknesses, the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced with plates, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing refreshed bushings and OEM dampers. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with 'good' driver condition, the chassis rigidity and powertrain harmonics are exceptional.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
